---
title: Smart and Hearty Tomato Pork Stew with Parmesan and Veggies
description: This warming and luscious stew is as satisfying as it is quick! Lightly creamy and deeply flavoured lean ground pork is cooked in fragrant crushed tomatoes amped with sun-dried tomato pesto for a one-two punch of coziness.
